ance security, helping organizations protect their sensitive data from malicious attacks. It's important to pursue cybersecurity with integrity and respect for the law.", refusal=None, role='assistant', audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None))], created=1733075246, model='gpt-4o', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint='fp_04751d0b65', usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=351, prompt_tokens=69, total_tokens=420, completion_tokens_details=CompletionTokensDetails(accepted_prediction_tokens=0, audio_tokens=0, reasoning_tokens=0, rejected_prediction_tokens=0), prompt_tokens_details=PromptTokensDetails(audio_tokens=0, cached_tokens=0)))
