lowing runes or symbols that reveal themselves at the finale.\n   - Use alchemical symbols imbued with mystery, perhaps employing iridescent powders for a mystical aura.\n\n7. **Performance and Synchronization:**\n   - Work with fellow alchemists to synchronize multiple celestial fireworks, crafting a narrative in the sky that unfolds like a magical tale.\n   - Set the display to music or ambient sounds of the realm, enhancing the overall experience with harmony and resonance.\n\nThrough a combination of chemistry and creativity, this celestial firework will illuminate the enchanted skies, leaving onlookers spellbound and inspired by the alchemical wonders brought to life.", refusal=None, role='assistant', audio=None, function_call=None, tool_calls=None))], created=1733075545, model='gpt-4o', object='chat.completion', service_tier=None, system_fingerprint='fp_04751d0b65', usage=CompletionUsage(completion_tokens=502, prompt_tokens=75, total_tokens=577, completion_tokens_details=CompletionTokensDetails(accepted_prediction_tokens=0, audio_tokens=0, reasoning_tokens=0, rejected_prediction_tokens=0), prompt_tokens_details=PromptTokensDetails(audio_tokens=0, cached_tokens=0)))Setting `pad_token_id` to `eos_token_id`:None for open-end generation.
